<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IDataArrayOutput.HasCapturedCounterValue" Title="HasCapturedCounterValue method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IDataArrayOutput">IDataArrayOutput</PageRef> ->
    HasCapturedCounterValue
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>HasCapturedCounterValue</TypeRef> method returns true if there is a captured counter value ready to be read from the output.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[bool HasCapturedCounterValue() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="bool">
        True if a counter value has been captured and can be read, false otherwise.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
